source: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_000<tab>Another anima glass? I could swear I saw you using the one I gave you not long ago.
target: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_000<tab>Vous avez besoin d'une autre <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8C6D0202 /var><var 1D /var>? Ha ha ha, <var 08 E905 (( sacrée Madame)) ((sacré Monsieur)) /var> <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, toujours le mot pour rire<var 1D /var>! Et qu'est-ce que je vois qui dépasse de votre sac, là, hein<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_001<tab>If they were more easily crafted I would gladly offer you another, but sadly that is not the case. That said, you are more than welcome to a replacement when you are truly in need.
target: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_001<tab>Si jamais il vous arrivait de <var 1A 02 /var>vraiment<var 1A 01 /var> la perdre, faites-le-moi savoir et je vous en donnerai une nouvelle.

source: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_011<tab>No need to fret. I have prepared another as a safety precaution. With so much at stake, one can never be too careful.
target: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_011<tab>Ne vous en faites pas, j'en ai plusieurs en réserve. Je peux vous en confier une toute neuve, si vous le désirez.

source: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_020<tab>If anything should happen to it, pray come and speak with me. I shall see to having another prepared for you.
target: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_020<tab>Tenez. Et tâchez d'en prendre soin, cette fois<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_030<tab>Are you certain? I imagine tracking the anima's progress will be difficult without it.
target: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_030<tab>Oh, vous n'en avez pas besoin<var 1D /var>? C'est pourtant un outil très utile, vous savez...

source: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_031<tab>Well, let me know should you change your mind.
target: TEXT_JOBREL500GETGLASSAGAIN_00374_ARDASHIR_000_031<tab>Si vous changez d'avis, n'hésitez surtout pas à me le faire savoir<var 1D /var>!
